</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/c6209362-0afd-11ec-90ec-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/2021-08-24T171837Z_1158252795_RC2TBP919OT1_RTRMADP_3_AFGHANISTAN-CONFLICT-CONTACT.JPG"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/c6209362-0afd-11ec-90ec-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/2021-08-24T171837Z_1158252795_RC2TBP919OT1_RTRMADP_3_AFGHANISTAN-CONFLICT-CONTACT.JPG" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">1d716936-0f1b-11ec-adbf-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Sep 2021 14:03:04 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/c6209362-0afd-11ec-90ec-005056a97e36/w:1024/p:16x9/2021-08-24T171837Z_1158252795_RC2TBP919OT1_RTRMADP_3_AFGHANISTAN-CONFLICT-CONTACT.JPG">© 路透社</source><dc:creator>方華</dc:creator></item><item><category>美洲</category><title>洪都拉斯大選：左派候選人稱如勝選將轉與中國建交</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B4%B2/20210906-%E6%B4%AA%E9%83%BD%E6%8B%89%E6%96%AF%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E5%B7%A6%E6%B4%BE%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%E7%A8%B1%E5%A6%82%E5%8B%9D%E9%81%B8%E5%B0%87%E8%BD%89%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%BA%E4%BA%A4</link><description>
